		<p><strong>U.S. Ski & Snowboard Coach </strong>with background screening ($135): leadership to athletes through U.S. Ski & Snowboard club programs. Every U.S. Ski & Snowboard Coach member undergoes periodic background screening to help provide a SafeSport environment in clubs. In addition, coaches are required to take a short online education program on important coaching guidelines. 
